'''肥胖症'''（{{lang|en|Obesity}}）是指體脂肪累積過多而對健康造成負面影響的身體狀態，可能導致壽命減短及各種健康問題<ref name="WHO 2000">{{cite book|author=World Health Organization (WHO)|title=Technical report series 894: Obesity: Preventing and managing the global epidemic.|location=Geneva|publisher=World Health Organization|year=2000|url=http://www.who.int/nutrition/publications/obesity/WHO_TRS_894/en/|format=PDF|isbn=92-4-120894-5|access-date=2016-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119073057/http://www.who.int/nutrition/publications/obesity/WHO_TRS_894/en/|archive-date=2016-01-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|9}}。肥胖與遺傳有關，也與生活方式相關；一些人可能因為基因之故而較不容易發胖，但不論是誰，任何人都有可能發胖，但反過來任何人也都有可能減重。<ref>{{cite news|author=KATIE MOISSE|title=Do Thin Parents Pass On Skinny Genes?|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Health/w_DietAndFitnessNews/thin-parents-pass-skinny-genes/story?id=14673043|accessdate=2021-07-25|work=ABC News Network|date=2011-10-05|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210201943/https://abcnews.go.com/Health/w_DietAndFitnessNews/thin-parents-pass-skinny-genes/story?id=14673043|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Scott Reall|title=Journey to Healthy Living: Freedom from Body Image and Food Issues|date=2008-04-15|publisher=Thomas Nelson|isbn=9781418574376|page=18}}</ref>

肥胖的標準常使用[[身體質量指數|身體質量指數]]（{{lang|en|BMI}}）來衡量，即以體重（公斤）除以身高（公尺）的平方<ref name="HaslamJames">{{Cite journal|title=Obesity|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16198769|last=Haslam|first=David W.|last2=James|first2=W. Philip T.|date=2005-10-01|journal=Lancet (London, England)|issue=9492|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(05)67483-1|volume=366|pages=1197–1209|issn=1474-547X|pmid=16198769|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2022-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220306075026/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16198769/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WHO 2000"/>{{rp|6}} 。西方人認為BMI大於{{val|30|ul=kg/m2}} 即為肥胖，介於25到{{val|30|ul=kg/m2}}間則為過重；一些东亚国家採用更严格的标准，例如中華民國[[行政院衛生署|行政院衛生署]]（今[[中華民國衛生福利部|衛生福利部]]）於2002年4月公布成人的BMI≧27 即為肥胖，24≦{{lang|en|BMI}}＜27 則為過重<ref>{{Cite web|title=BMI 測試|url=http://health99.hpa.gov.tw/OnlinkHealth/Onlink_BMI.aspx|accessdate=2015-11-19|publisher=衛生福利部國民健康署|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117020731/http://health99.hpa.gov.tw/OnlinkHealth/Onlink_BMI.aspx|archive-date=2015-11-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但幼兒並不適合用成人的{{lang|en|BMI}}標準來評量<ref>{{cite book|author=Peter G. Kopelman, Ian D. Caterson, Michael J. Stock, William H. Dietz|title=Clinical obesity in adults and children: In Adults and Children|url=https://archive.org/details/clinicalobesityi02edunse|publisher=Blackwell Publishing|location=|year=2005|pages=[https://archive.org/details/clinicalobesityi02edunse/page/12 12]–28|isbn=1-4051-1672-2}}</ref>。

肥胖會增加[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]、[[2型糖尿病|2型糖尿病]]、[[睡眠呼吸中止症|睡眠呼吸中止症]]、某些[[癌症|癌症]]、[[退化性關節炎|退化性關節炎]]及其他疾病的發生機會<ref name="HaslamJames" />。而造成肥胖的主因常包括[[熱量|熱量]]攝取過多、欠缺[[運動|運動]]及體質問題等，其他如基因缺陷、內分泌異常、藥物影響及精神疾病也可能造成肥胖。有種說法認為「肥胖的人由於[[代謝|代謝]]慢，因此即使吃得不多也會越來越胖」，但目前的科學證據傾向不支持此種論點。由於維持體重增加所需的能量，肥胖者的能量消耗比正常人多<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=vWjK5etS7PMC&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN|publisher=Humana Press|date=2007-10-18|isbn=978-1-59745-400-1|language=en|first=Robert F.|last=Kushner|first2=Daniel H.|last2=Bessesen|title=Treatment of the Obese Patient|pages=158|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210202007/https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=vWjK5etS7PMC&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Anes2000">{{Cite journal|title=Obesity in anaesthesia and intensive care|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10927998|last=Adams|first=J. P.|last2=Murphy|first2=P. G.|date=2000-07|journal=British Journal of Anaesthesia|issue=1|doi=10.1093/bja/85.1.91|volume=85|pages=91–108|issn=0007-0912|pmid=10927998|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2022-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220222225343/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10927998/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

肥胖可以由個人選擇結合社會變革共同預防。肥胖的主要治療方式有[[節食|飲食計畫]]和[[體能鍛煉|運動]]。患者在日常飲食中必須避免高熱量（高油高糖）食物並增加高[[膳食纖維|纖]]食物，若良好的飲食控制無法有效減重，則可以考慮搭配{{le|抗肥胖藥物|Anti-obesity medication}}來減低食慾和抑制脂肪吸收。如果飲食、運動、甚至搭配藥物都不見效，用來減少胃容積的[[胃內水球置放術|胃內水球置放術]]可能會有幫助，以[[手術|手術]]來減少胃容積或腸道長度也能直接降低食量並減少營養素的吸收<ref>NICE 2006 p.10–11</ref><ref name="balloon2008">{{Cite journal|title=Safety and effectiveness of the intragastric balloon for obesity. A meta-analysis|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18459025|last=Imaz|first=Iñaki|last2=Martínez-Cervell|first2=Carmen|date=2008-07|journal=Obesity Surgery|issue=7|doi=10.1007/s11695-007-9331-8|volume=18|pages=841–846|issn=0960-8923|pmid=18459025|last3=García-Alvarez|first3=Elvira Elena|last4=Sendra-Gutiérrez|first4=Juan Manuel|last5=González-Enríquez|first5=Jesús|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2022-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220316102204/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18459025/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

肥胖是全世界主要的{{le|可預防死因|Preventable causes of death}}<ref name="WHO2015">{{cite web|title=Obesity and overweight  Fact sheet N°311|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs311/en/|accessdate=2 February 2016|date=January 2015|website=WHO|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180422005225/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs311/en/|archive-date=2018-04-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是21世紀最重要的[[公共衛生|公共衛生]]問題之一<ref name="Dibaise2013">{{Cite journal|title=Role of the gastroenterologist in managing obesity|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23899283|last=Dibaise|first=John K.|last2=Foxx-Orenstein|first2=Amy E.|date=2013-07|journal=Expert Review of Gastroenterology & Hepatology|issue=5|doi=10.1586/17474124.2013.811061|volume=7|pages=439–451|issn=1747-4132|pmid=23899283|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2022-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308172235/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23899283/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前成人與[[兒童|兒童]]的肥胖盛行率都在上升，且女性較男性更常發生。2015年，全球有6億名成人（13%）和4200萬名五歲以下的孩童有肥胖問題<ref name=WHO2015 />。在現代世界的許多地方（尤其是[[西方世界|西方國家]]）受到汙名化，儘管在歷史上的其他時候，肥胖常被視為財富與多產的象徵，並且在世界的某些地區仍然如此<ref name="HaslamJames" /><ref name=Woodhouse/>。2013年，包括[[美國醫學會|美國醫學會]]和美國心臟協會等數個醫學會將肥胖定義為一種[[疾病|疾病]]<ref name="NYTimes20130618">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/19/business/ama-recognizes-obesity-as-a-disease.html?_r=0|title=A.M.A. Recognizes Obesity as a Disease|last=Pollack|first=Andrew|date=2013-06-18|newspaper=New York Times|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Hav05TK0?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/19/business/ama-recognizes-obesity-as-a-disease.html?_r=1|archivedate=2013-06-23|deadurl=yes|access-date=2015-11-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Facts About Obesity|url=http://www.hhnmag.com/hhnmag/HHNDaily/HHNDailyDisplay.dhtml?id=5870001020|accessdate=2013-06-24|date=2013-06-21|website=H&HN|publisher=American Hospital Association|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130909051439/http://www.hhnmag.com/hhnmag/HHNDaily/HHNDailyDisplay.dhtml?id=5870001020|archive-date=2013-09-09|dead-url=no|last1=Weinstock|first1=Matthew}}</ref>。

==定義==
