[[File:Obesity6.JPG|thumb]]
肥胖指的是體脂肪過度堆積而對健康造成負面影響的身體狀態<ref name="WHO 2000"/>{{rp|6}}。肥胖最初的定義以[[身體質量指數|身體質量指數]]（{{lang|en|Body Mass Index, BMI}}）為指標，之後也加入了其他標準，例如評估[[腰臀比|腰臀比]]或其他心血管病症風險因子<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Measurement and Definitions of Obesity In Childhood and Adolescence: A field guide for the uninitiated|url=http://nutritionj.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1475-2891-6-32|last=Sweeting|first=Helen N|date=2007-12|journal=Nutrition Journal|issue=1|doi=10.1186/1475-2891-6-32|volume=6|pages=32|language=en|issn=1475-2891|pmc=PMC2164947|pmid=17963490|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2022-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220319232014/https://nutritionj.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1475-2891-6-32|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nhlbi"/>{{rp|14}}。BMI與[[體脂肪率|體脂肪率]]和體脂肪總量都密切相關<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Use of relative weight and Body Mass Index for the determination of adiposity|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/2037859|last=Gray|first=D. S.|last2=Fujioka|first2=K.|date=1991|journal=Journal of Clinical Epidemiology|issue=6|doi=10.1016/0895-4356(91)90218-x|volume=44|pages=545–550|issn=0895-4356|pmid=2037859|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210195927/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/2037859/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兒童的健康體重因性別與年齡而有不同的標準，此標準需透過與同年齡性別的其他孩子（常模）比較來決定。舉例而言，兒童與青少年的肥胖定義為BMI高於95%的同儕（95[[百分位數|百分位]]以上）<ref name="cdc.gov">{{cite web |url=http://www.cdc.gov/nccdphp/dnpa/healthyweight/assessing/bmi/childrens_BMI/about_childrens_BMI.htm |title=Healthy Weight: Assessing Your Weight: BMI: About BMI for Children and Teens |publisher=Center for disease control and prevention |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612034846/https://www.cdc.gov/nccdphp/dnpa/healthyweight/assessing/bmi/childrens_BMI/about_childrens_BMI.htm |archive-date=2019-06-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。用於決定兒童與青少年肥胖與否的常模資料來自1963年至1994年，因此並沒有反映近年平均體重的上升<ref name="Flegal KM, Ogden CL, Wei R, Kuczmarski RL, Johnson CL 2001 1086–93">{{Cite journal|title=Prevalence of overweight in US children: comparison of US growth charts from the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention with other reference values for body mass index|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11382664|last=Flegal|first=K. M.|last2=Ogden|first2=C. L.|date=2001-06|journal=The American Journal of Clinical Nutrition|issue=6|doi=10.1093/ajcn/73.6.1086|volume=73|pages=1086–1093|issn=0002-9165|pmid=11382664|last3=Wei|first3=R.|last4=Kuczmarski|first4=R. L.|last5=Johnson|first5=C. L.|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2022-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220303000152/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11382664/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 身體質量指數 ===
身體質量指數定義為體重（公斤）除以身高的平方（公尺）：
:<math>\mathrm{BMI}= \frac{mass}{height^2}</math>
式子中的mass是體重，height是身高。BMI通常以公斤/平方公尺為單位，若以英制單位（磅與吋）計算，則應該再乘以703（公斤/平方公尺）/（磅/平方吋）。

