[[體脂肪率|體脂肪率]]則是脂肪含量占总体重的百分比，一般认为男性体脂大於25%或女性大於33%即為肥胖<ref name=emedicine>{{cite web |url=http://www.emedicine.com/med/TOPIC1653.HTM |author=Schwarz, Steven |title=Obesity |accessdate=2008-09-30 |work= |publisher=emedicine |date=2007-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919012112/http://www.emedicine.com/med/topic1653.htm |archive-date=2008-09-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。體脂肪率可通过以下公式用BMI的数值进行计算：

:体脂<math>\% = 1.2 \times BMI + 0.23 \times</math>年龄<math> - 5.4 - 10.8 \times</math>性别

其中男性性别取值为1，女性取0。该公式考虑到在相等BMI的情形下，男性体脂含量比后者低約10%；且即使體重不變，體脂肪率也會隨著年齡增长<ref name=Kopelman2005 />。

== 肥胖症發生的時期 ==
人類一生中，有三個發胖的關鍵期，分別為：胎嬰期、少年期、中年期。胎嬰期是在母體內的胎兒與產後的嬰兒時期，母體攝取的熱量過多、或餵食牛乳等，影響胎嬰的脂肪細胞增生較多<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Size at birth, childhood growth and obesity in adult life|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11360158/|last=Eriksson|first=J.|last2=Forsén|first2=T.|date=2001-05|journal=International Journal of Obesity and Related Metabolic Disorders: Journal of the International Association for the Study of Obesity|issue=5|doi=10.1038/sj.ijo.0801602|volume=25|pages=735–740|pmid=11360158|last3=Tuomilehto|first3=J.|last4=Osmond|first4=C.|last5=Barker|first5=D.|access-date=2021-09-18|archive-date=2022-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121065510/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11360158/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。少年期主要是生長激素分泌旺盛的長高期，生長激素除了促進骨頭生長也促進脂肪分解以提供能量給肌肉骨骼成長<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Predicting Obesity in Young Adulthood from Childhood and Parental Obesity|url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/abs/10.1056/NEJM199709253371301|last=Whitaker|first=Robert C.|last2=Wright|first2=Jeffrey A.|date=1997-09-25|journal=New England Journal of Medicine|issue=13|doi=10.1056/NEJM199709253371301|volume=337|pages=869–873|language=en|issn=0028-4793|pmid=9302300|last3=Pepe|first3=Margaret S.|last4=Seidel|first4=Kristy D.|last5=Dietz|first5=William H.}}</ref>。中年期基礎代謝遞減，活動量較少，且經濟能力較佳而食用高熱量美食，此時腹圍增加、內臟脂肪累積，且易生骨減肌少性肥胖（osteosarcopenic obesity，OSO）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Obesity in midlife: lifestyle and dietary strategies|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31576760/|last=Khandelwal|first=S.|date=2020-04|journal=Climacteric: The Journal of the International Menopause Society|issue=2|doi=10.1080/13697137.2019.1660638|volume=23|pages=140–147|issn=1473-0804|pmid=31576760|access-date=2021-09-18|archive-date=2022-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124085500/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31576760/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Osteosarcopenic Obesity: Current Knowledge, Revised Identification Criteria and Treatment Principles|url=https://www.mdpi.com/2072-6643/11/4/747|last=Kelly|first=Owen|last2=Gilman|first2=Jennifer|date=2019-03-30|journal=Nutrients|issue=4|doi=10.3390/nu11040747|volume=11|pages=747|language=en|issn=2072-6643|pmc=PMC6520721|pmid=30935031|last3=Boschiero|first3=Dario|last4=Ilich|first4=Jasminka|access-date=2021-11-14|archive-date=2022-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220301142415/https://www.mdpi.com/2072-6643/11/4/747|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 肥胖症对健康的影响 ==
體重過重與許多疾病的發生相關，包括[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]、[[第2型糖尿病|第2型糖尿病]]、[[睡眠呼吸中止症|睡眠呼吸中止症]]、某些[[癌|癌]]症、[[退化性關節炎|退化性關節炎]]、以及[[氣喘|氣喘]]<ref name=HaslamJames/><ref name="Poulain">{{cite journal|title=The effect of obesity on chronic respiratory diseases: pathophysiology and therapeutic strategies|author=Poulain M, Doucet M, Major GC, Drapeau V, Sériès F, Boulet LP, Tremblay A, Maltais F|url=http://www.cmaj.ca/cgi/content/full/174/9/1293|date=2006-04|journal=CMAJ|issue=9|doi=10.1503/cmaj.051299|volume=174|pages=1293–9|pmc=1435949|pmid=16636330|access-date=2008-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610220733/http://www.cmaj.ca/cgi/content/full/174/9/1293|archive-date=2011-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由於上述疾病的緣故，研究也顯示肥胖者的預期餘命較短<ref name=HaslamJames/>。

