不同的區域與國家的人均{{le|飲食熱量攝取|Dietary energy supply}}差別很大，並會隨著時代而有明顯改變。從1970年代早期到1990年代晚期，除了東歐地區外，全球的人均每日熱量攝取（購買的食物量）都在上升。1996年，人均每日熱量供應最高的國家是美國，高達{{convert|3654|Cal}}，到了2003年更來到了{{convert|3754|Cal}}。1990年代晚期，歐洲人平均每人每日購買{{convert|3394|Cal}}的食物，而亞洲的[[開發中國家|開發中國家]]每人每日的食物購入量有{{convert|2648|Cal}}，而[[撒哈拉以南非洲|撒哈拉以南非洲]]則是{{convert|2176|Cal}}<ref name=Earth09/>。總熱量的攝取量與肥胖的發生有關<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/82-003-x/2009004/article/10933-eng.htm |title=Diet composition and obesity among Canadian adults |work=Statistics Canada |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180422120844/http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/82-003-x/2009004/article/10933-eng.htm |archive-date=2018-04-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

即使現在的{{le|飲食指引列表|List of nutrition guides|飲食指引}}相當普及<ref>{{cite web |author=National Control for Health Statistics |title=Nutrition For Everyone |publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention |url=http://www.cdc.gov/nccdphp/dnpa/nutrition/nutrition_for_everyone |accessdate=2008-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080821001216/http://www.cdc.gov/nccdphp/dnpa/nutrition/nutrition_for_everyone/ |archive-date=2008-08-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但飲食過量與飲食內容不健康的問題卻未因此改善<ref>{{cite journal | author = Marantz PR, Bird ED, Alderman MH | title = A call for higher standards of evidence for dietary guidelines | journal = Am J Prev Med | volume = 34 | issue = 3 | pages = 234–40 | date = 2008-03 | pmid = 18312812 | doi = 10.1016/j.amepre.2007.11.017 | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-preventive-medicine_2008-03_34_3/page/234}}</ref>。自1971年到2000年，美國的肥胖率從14.5%爬升到30.9%<ref name=Flegal2002>{{cite journal | author = Flegal KM, Carroll MD, Ogden CL, Johnson CL | title = Prevalence and trends in obesity among US adults, 1999–2000 | journal = JAMA | volume = 288 | issue = 14 | pages = 1723–1727 | date = 2002-10 | pmid = 12365955 | doi = 10.1001/jama.288.14.1723 | url = http://jama.ama-assn.org/cgi/content/full/288/14/1723 | access-date = 2008-12-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101109165730/http://jama.ama-assn.org/cgi/content/full/288/14/1723 | archive-date = 2010-11-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而平均的熱量攝取也在同期上升。女性的每日熱量攝取從1971年的{{convert|1542|Cal}}到2004年的{{convert|1877|Cal}}，平均上升了{{convert|335|Cal}}；而男性從1971年的{{convert|2450|Cal}}到2004年的{{convert|2618|Cal}}，平均增加了{{convert|168|Cal}}。飲食熱量的上升主要來自於[[碳水化合物|碳水化合物]]攝取量的上升，而非[[油脂|油脂]]攝取的上升<ref>{{cite journal | author = Wright JD, Kennedy-Stephenson J, Wang CY, McDowell MA, Johnson CL | title = Trends in intake of energy and macronutrients—United States, 1971–2000 | journal = MMWR Morb Mortal Wkly Rep | volume = 53 | issue = 4 | pages = 80–2 | date = 2004-02 | pmid = 14762332 | url = http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm5304a3.htm | access-date = 2008-12-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190620025227/https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm5304a3.htm | archive-date = 2019-06-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，多出來的[[碳水化合物|碳水化合物]]主要來自含糖飲料和[[馬鈴薯片|馬鈴薯片]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Changes in Diet and Lifestyle and Long-Term Weight Gain in Women and Men|author=Mozaffarian D, Hao T, Rimm EB, Willett WC, Hu FB|date=2011-06-23|journal=The New England Journal of Medicine|issue=25|doi=10.1056/NEJMoa1014296|volume=364|pages=2392–404|type=Meta-analysis|pmc=3151731|pmid=21696306}}</ref>。現代美國年輕人的飲食中，含糖飲料佔了每日熱量攝取的近四分之一<ref name=Caballero>{{cite journal | author = Caballero B | title = The global epidemic of obesity: An overview | journal = Epidemiol Rev | volume = 29 | issue =  | pages = 1–5 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17569676 | doi = 10.1093/epirev/mxm012 | url =  }}</ref>；一般認為碳酸飲料、調味果汁、調味茶、運動及能量飲品等含糖飲料在肥胖率的上升中居功厥偉<ref>{{cite journal | author = Malik VS, Schulze MB, Hu FB | title = Intake of sugar-sweetened beverages and weight gain: a systematic review | journal = Am. J. Clin. Nutr. | volume = 84 | issue = 2 | pages = 274–88 | date = 2006-08 | pmid = 16895873 | pmc = 3210834 | doi =  | url = http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/84/2/274 | type = Review | access-date = 2016-01-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101006020852/http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/84/2/274 | archive-date = 2010-10-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Olsen NJ, Heitmann BL | title = Intake of calorically sweetened beverages and obesity | journal = Obes Rev | volume = 10 | issue = 1 | pages = 68–75 | date = 2009-01 | pmid = 18764885 | doi = 10.1111/j.1467-789X.2008.00523.x | type = Review }}</ref>，並造成[[代謝症候群|代謝症候群]]與[[第2型糖尿病|第2型糖尿病]]的風險上升<ref>{{cite journal |author=Malik VS, Popkin BM, Bray GA, Després JP, Willett WC, Hu FB |title=Sugar-sweetened beverages and risk of metabolic syndrome and type 2 diabetes: a meta-analysis |journal=Diabetes Care |volume=33 |issue=11 |pages=2477–83 |date=2010-11  |pmid=20693348 |pmc=2963518 |doi=10.2337/dc10-1079 |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_diabetes-care_2010-11_33_11/page/2477|type=Meta-analysis, Review}}</ref>。

隨著社會變得越來越依賴[[食物熱量|熱量密度]]高、份量大的[[速食|速食]]餐點，速食與肥胖的關聯性變得越來越令人在意<ref>{{cite journal | author = Rosenheck R | title = Fast food consumption and increased caloric intake: a systematic review of a trajectory towards weight gain and obesity risk | journal = Obes Rev | volume = 9 | issue = 6 | pages = 535–47 | date = 2008-11 | pmid = 18346099 | doi = 10.1111/j.1467-789X.2008.00477.x | url = | type = Review }}</ref>。自1977年至1995間，美國的速食食用量成長了三倍，而來自速食的熱量則成長了四倍之多<ref>{{cite book |author=Lin BH, Guthrie J and Frazao E |editor=Frazão E |title=Agriculture Information Bulletin No. 750: America's Eating Habits: Changes and Consequences |url=http://www.ers.usda.gov/publications/aib-agricultural-information-bulletin/aib750.aspx |year=1999 |publisher=US Department of Agriculture, Economic Research Service |location=Washington, DC |pages=213–239 |chapter=Nutrient contribution of food away from home |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120708043622/http://www.ers.usda.gov/publications/aib-agricultural-information-bulletin/aib750.aspx |archivedate=2012-07-08 |access-date=2016-01-06 }}</ref>。

歐美的[[農業政策|農業政策]]與[[绿色革命|技術]]使糧食價格下滑。美國基於{{le|美國農業法案|United States farm bill|農業法案}}對玉米、大豆、小麥、以及米補助，造成加工食品在價格上低於蔬果<ref>{{cite news |author=Pollan, Michael |title=You Are What You Grow |work=New York Times |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/04/22/magazine/22wwlnlede.t.html?ex=1186027200&en=bbe0f6a2c10e3b3c&ei=5070 |date=2007-04-22 |accessdate=2007-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109040407/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/04/22/magazine/22wwlnlede.t.html?ex=1186027200&en=bbe0f6a2c10e3b3c&ei=5070 |archive-date=2012-11-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。近年來國家開始制定{{le|熱量標示法令|Calorie count laws|熱量標示}}與[[營養標籤|食品成份標示]]的相關法令，希望能使人們選擇較為健康的食物，並提升對自身熱量攝取的關心。

相對於正常體重者，肥胖者傾向於將自己的食量說得較低<ref>{{cite book|author=Peter G. Kopelman, Ian D. Caterson, Michael J. Stock, William H. Dietz |title=Clinical obesity in adults and children: In Adults and Children |url=https://archive.org/details/clinicalobesityi02edunse |publisher=Blackwell Publishing |location= |year=2005 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/clinicalobesityi02edunse/page/324 324] |isbn=1-4051-1672-2}}</ref> ，以[[热量计|熱量計]]測量受試者的研究<ref>{{cite book|title=Metabolism alone doesn't explain how thin people stay thin |publisher=The Medical Post |work=John Schieszer}}</ref>與直接的觀察性研究都支持這個現象的存在。

=== 坐式生活型態 ===

[[坐式生活型態|坐式生活型態]]在肥胖症的发病过程中起重要作用<ref name = "Kopelman2005"/>{{rp|10}}。肥胖症患者的活动量较体重正常的人少，例如在加拿大，[[生活型態|生活方式]]为坐式的男性27%患有肥胖症，但正常活动量的男性仅有19.6%患有肥胖症<ref name=Tjepkema2005>{{cite book | author=Tjepkema M | chapter=Measured Obesity–Adult obesity in Canada: Measured height and weight | title=Nutrition: Findings from the Canadian Community Health Survey | publisher=Statistics Canada | date=2005-07-06 | location=Ottawa, Ontario | url=http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/82-620-m/2005001/article/adults-adultes/8060-eng.htm | access-date=2016-09-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108103230/http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/82-620-m/2005001/article/adults-adultes/8060-eng.htm | archive-date=2016-11-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

世界各地都可看到工作體力需求減少的現象<ref name=WHO2009>{{cite web |url=http://www.who.int/dietphysicalactivity/publications/facts/obesity/en/ |title=WHO: Obesity and overweight |work=World Health Organization |accessdate=2009-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081218104805/http://www.who.int/dietphysicalactivity/publications/facts/obesity/en/ |archivedate=2008-12-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=WHOExercise>{{cite web |url=http://www.who.int/dietphysicalactivity/factsheet_inactivity/en/index.html |title=WHO | Physical Inactivity: A Global Public Health Problem |work=[[World_Health_Organization|World Health Organization]] |accessdate=2009-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140213190030/http://www.who.int/dietphysicalactivity/factsheet_inactivity/en/index.html |archive-date=2014-02-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Ness2006>{{cite journal | author = Ness-Abramof R, Apovian CM | title = Diet modification for treatment and prevention of obesity | journal = Endocrine | volume = 29 | issue = 1 | pages = 5–9 | date = 2006-02 | pmid = 16622287 | doi = 10.1385/ENDO:29:1:135 | url = | type = Review }}</ref>，至少有30%的人生活中的運動量不足<ref name=WHOExercise/>。這主要是由於在移動時搭乘交通工具的機會增加，且協助在家中省力的新技術也增加<ref name=WHO2009/><ref name=WHOExercise/><ref name=Ness2006/>。中国有一项研究表明，[[都市化|城市化]]导致每日能量支出减少300-400kcal，以车代步则使每日能量支出又减少200kcal。<ref name=James2008/>。運動量下降的現象在兒童身上也能看到，主因是走路的機會變少，且體育課的量也下降<ref>{{cite journal | author = Salmon J, Timperio A | title = Prevalence, trends and environmental influences on child and youth physical activity | journal = Med Sport Sci | volume = 50 | issue =  | pages = 183–99 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17387258 | doi = 10.1159/000101391 | isbn = 978-3-318-01396-2 | series = Medicine and Sport Science | type = Review }}</ref>。人們將休閒時間花在運動的比例是否有下降則不那麼明朗。[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]指出人們在娛樂活動中消耗的體力正在減少，但在芬蘭的研究<ref>{{cite journal | author = Borodulin K, Laatikainen T, Juolevi A, Jousilahti P | title = Thirty-year trends of physical activity in relation to age, calendar time and birth cohort in Finnish adults | journal = Eur J Public Health | volume = 18 | issue = 3 | pages = 339–44 | date = 2008-06 | pmid = 17875578 | doi = 10.1093/eurpub/ckm092 | url = | type = Research Support }}</ref>卻得到相反的結論，至於在美國的研究則發現美國人在娛樂活動中消耗的體力並沒有明顯變化<ref>{{cite journal | author = Brownson RC, Boehmer TK, Luke DA | title = Declining rates of physical activity in the United States: what are the contributors? | journal = Annu Rev Public Health | volume = 26 | issue =  | pages = 421–43 | year = 2005 | pmid = 15760296 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.publhealth.26.021304.144437 | url = | type = Review }}</ref>。

不論在兒童或成人，看電視的時間與肥胖的風險都有關聯<ref>{{cite journal | author = Gortmaker SL, Must A, Sobol AM, Peterson K, Colditz GA, Dietz WH | title = Television viewing as a cause of increasing obesity among children in the United States, 1986–1990 | journal = Arch Pediatr Adolesc Med | volume = 150 | issue = 4 | pages = 356–62 | date = 1996-04 | pmid = 8634729 | doi = 10.1001/archpedi.1996.02170290022003 | type = Review }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Vioque J, Torres A, Quiles J | title = Time spent watching television, sleep duration and obesity in adults living in Valencia, Spain | journal = Int. J. Obes. Relat. Metab. Disord. | volume = 24 | issue = 12 | pages = 1683–8 | date = 2000-12 | pmid = 11126224 | doi = 10.1038/sj.ijo.0801434 | url = | type = Research Support }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Tucker LA, Bagwell M | title = Television viewing and obesity in adult females | journal = Am J Public Health | volume = 81 | issue = 7 | pages = 908–11 | date = 1991-07 | pmid = 2053671 | pmc = 1405200 | doi = 10.2105/AJPH.81.7.908 | url = http://www.ajph.org/cgi/reprint/81/7/908 | format = PDF | access-date = 2016-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081202121420/http://www.ajph.org/cgi/reprint/81/7/908 | archive-date = 2008-12-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一篇評論性文章指出，在針對兒童肥胖的73個研究中，有63個（86%）都發現兒童和媒體的接觸頻率與兒童的肥胖率會同步上升，且上升的程度與看電視的時間成正相關<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ipsdweb.ipsd.org/uploads/IPPC/CSM%20Media%20Health%20Report.pdf |title=Media + Child and Adolescent Health: A Systematic Review |publisher=Common Sense Media |year=2008 |format=PDF |work=Ezekiel J. Emanuel |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121122070205/http://ipsdweb.ipsd.org/uploads/IPPC/CSM%20Media%20Health%20Report.pdf |archive-date=2012-11-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 遗传因素 ===
<!--{{Main|Genetics of obesity}}-->
[[File:La_monstrua_desnuda_(1680),_de_Juan_Carreño_de_Miranda..jpg|thumb]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.esst.org/newsletter2000.htm |title=Case Study: Cataplexy and SOREMPs Without Excessive Daytime Sleepiness in Prader Willi Syndrome. Is This the Beginning of Narcolepsy in a Five Year Old? |author=Mary Jones |publisher=European Society of Sleep Technologists |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606223122/http://www.esst.org/newsletter2000.htm |archive-date=2017-06-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>]]
如同許多疾病，肥胖是基因與環境因子互動所產生的結果。控制[[食慾|食慾]]與[[代謝|代謝]]的[[基因|基因]]決定了人們在食物不虞匱乏時是否會有肥胖症狀。至2006年為止，已認定人類基因體上有超過41個基因在特定情形下會造成肥胖<ref>{{cite journal | author = Poirier P, Giles TD, Bray GA, Hong Y, Stern JS, Pi-Sunyer FX, Eckel RH | title = Obesity and cardiovascular disease: pathophysiology, evaluation, and effect of weight loss | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_arteriosclerosis-thrombosis-and-vascular-biology_2006-05_26_5/page/968 | journal = Arterioscler. Thromb. Vasc. Biol. | volume = 26 | issue = 5 | pages = 968–76 | date = 2006-05 | pmid = 16627822 | doi = 10.1161/01.ATV.0000216787.85457.f3 | type = Review }}</ref>。擁有兩套[[FTO基因|肥胖基因]]（脂肪與肥胖關聯基因）的人比常人平均重了3-4公斤，患上肥胖的機率是沒有該[[等位基因|等位基因]]者的1.67倍<ref>{{cite journal | author = Loos RJ, Bouchard C | title = FTO: the first gene contributing to common forms of human obesity | journal = Obes Rev | volume = 9 | issue = 3 | pages = 246–50 | date = 2008-05 | pmid = 18373508 | doi = 10.1111/j.1467-789X.2008.00481.x | url = | type = Review }}</ref>。因遺傳造成的BMI差異會隨族群而不同，差異可以6%至85%<ref>{{cite journal | author = Yang W, Kelly T, He J | title = Genetic epidemiology of obesity | journal = Epidemiol Rev | volume = 29 | issue = | pages = 49–61 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17566051 | doi = 10.1093/epirev/mxm004 | type = Review }}</ref>。

肥胖是幾個症候群的主要特徵，比如說[[普瑞德威利症候群|普瑞德威利症候群]]（俗稱小胖威利症候群）、[[巴德-畢德氏症候群|巴德-畢德氏症候群]]、[[科恩綜合症|科恩症候群]]、以及{{le|MOMO症候群|MOMO syndrome}}；因此有時會用「非症候群相關的肥胖」這個名詞來排除這些疾病造成的肥胖<ref name="pmid19506576">{{cite journal | author = Walley AJ, Asher JE, Froguel P | title = The genetic contribution to non-syndromic human obesity | journal = Nature Reviews Genetics | volume = 10 | issue = 7 | pages = 431–42 | date =  2009-06 | pmid = 19506576 | doi = 10.1038/nrg2594 | url = | type = Review }}</ref>。患有早發性嚴重肥胖的人（其定義為在十歲前就發生肥胖，且BMI較平均高出3個標準差以上）有7%帶有[[單核苷酸多態性|核苷酸的單點突變]]（SNP）<ref>{{cite journal | author = Farooqi S, O'Rahilly S | title = Genetics of obesity in humans | journal = Endocr. Rev. | volume = 27 | issue = 7 | pages = 710–18 | date = 2006-12 | pmid = 17122358 | doi = 10.1210/er.2006-0040 | url = http://edrv.endojournals.org/cgi/content/full/27/7/710 | type = Review | access-date = 2008-12-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100710170521/http://edrv.endojournals.org/cgi/content/full/27/7/710 | archive-date = 2010-07-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

具有FTO基因的人若定期進行中等强度体力活动（相当于3-4小时的快步行走）时，罹患肥胖的機率就會下降<ref>{{cite journal | author=Rampersaud E, Mitchell BD, Pollin TI ''et al.'' | title=Physical activity and the association of common FTO gene variants with body mass index and obesity | journal=Arch Intern Med | year=2008 | volume=16 | pages=1791–97 | doi=10.1001/archinte.168.16.1791 | pmid=18779467}}</ref>。有一个研究表明肥胖父母的后代有80%也是肥胖症患者，而体重正常父母的后代只有10%是肥胖症患者。<ref name=Kopelman2005>{{cite book|author=Peter G. Kopelman, Ian D. Caterson,  Michael J. Stock,  William H. Dietz|title=Clinical obesity in adults and children: In Adults and Children|publisher=Blackwell Publishing|location=|year=2005|pages=493|isbn=140-511672-2|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=u7RvldSr5M0C|access-date=2008-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023073301/http://books.google.ca/books?id=u7RvldSr5M0C|archive-date=2012-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Kolata2007/>不同的人處在同樣的環境時，也會因為他們的基因差異而有不同的肥胖風險<ref>{{cite journal | author = Walley, Andrew J., Asher, Julian E., Froguel, Philippe | title = The genetic contribution to non-syndromic human obesity. | journal = Nat Rev Genet. | volume = 10 | issue = 7 | pages = 431–42 | date = 2009-07 | pmid = 19506576 | doi = 10.1038/nrg2594 | url = http://www.nature.com/nrg/journal/v10/n7/full/nrg2594.html | type = Review | quote = However, it is also clear that genetics greatly influences this situation, giving individuals in the same 'obesogenic' environment significantly different risks of becoming obese. | access-date = 2016-01-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110608213330/http://www.nature.com/nrg/journal/v10/n7/full/nrg2594.html | archive-date = 2011-06-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

{{le|节约基因理论|thrifty gene hypothesis}}假设在相同的环境条件下，某些特定的种族或人群比较容易发生肥胖。他们能充分吸收食物中的能量并以脂肪的形式储存，以适应环境的改变（例如[[飢荒|飢荒]]）及自然选择的压力。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Chakravarthy MV, Booth FW |title=Eating, exercise, and "thrifty" genotypes: Connecting the dots toward an evolutionary understanding of modern chronic diseases |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-applied-physiology_2004-01_96_1/page/3 |journal=J. Appl. Physiol. |volume=96 |issue=1 |pages=3–10 |year=2004 |pmid=14660491 |doi=10.1152/japplphysiol.00757.2003}}</ref>，但在食物供應穩定的環境下，這種儲存脂肪的能力卻會變成一種適應障礙<ref>{{cite journal | author = Chakravarthy MV, Booth FW | title = Eating, exercise, and "thrifty" genotypes: Connecting the dots toward an evolutionary understanding of modern chronic diseases | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-applied-physiology_2004-01_96_1/page/3 | journal = J. Appl. Physiol. | volume = 96 | issue = 1 | pages = 3–10 | year = 2004 | pmid = 14660491 | doi = 10.1152/japplphysiol.00757.2003 | type = Review }}</ref>。有學者認為就是为什么一些在沙漠中生活的{{le|Pima印地安人|Pima people}}在西方生活方式下會发生严重肥胖<ref name=Pool2001/>。節儉基因假說受到不少批評，另外也有許多其他基於演化的假說提出（例如{{le|基因漂移假說|drifty gene hypothesis}}與{{le|節儉表型理論|thrifty phenotype}}<ref>{{cite journal | author = Wells JC | title = Thrift: A guide to thrifty genes, thrifty phenotypes and thrifty norms | journal = International Journal of Obesity | volume = 33 | issue = 12 | pages = 1331–1338 | year = 2009 | pmid = 19752875 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1038/ijo.2009.175 | type = Review }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Wells JC | title = The thrifty phenotype: An adaptation in growth or metabolism? | journal = American Journal of Human Biology | volume = 23 | issue = 1 | pages = 65–75 | year = 2011 | pmid = 21082685 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1002/ajhb.21100 | type = Review }}</ref>。

=== 生理和心理疾病的影响 ===
某些生理或心理疾病以及治疗它们的药物會增加患者罹患肥胖症的風險。生理疾病包括上述的罕见遗传病，以及一些先天或後天疾病，比如[[甲状腺功能低下|甲状腺功能低下]]、[[库兴氏综合症|库欣综合征]]、{{le|生长激素缺乏症|Growth hormone deficiency}}等<ref>{{cite journal |author=Rosén T, Bosaeus I, Tölli J, Lindstedt G, Bengtsson BA |title=Increased body fat mass and decreased extracellular fluid volume in adults with growth hormone deficiency |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_clinical-endocrinology_1993-01_38_1/page/63 |journal=Clin. Endocrinol. (Oxf) |volume=38 |issue=1 |pages=63–71 |year=1993 |pmid=8435887| doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2265.1993.tb00974.x}}</ref>，另外也包括了[[进食障碍|进食障碍]]（如[[过胖暴食症|暴食障碍]]和{{le|夜间进食综合征|night eating syndrome}}）<ref name=HaslamJames/>。即使肥胖與部分的精神疾病相關，但肥胖不被視為精神疾病，因此并未将其列入[[精神障碍诊断与统计手册|精神障碍诊断与统计手册]]<ref name=Kolata2007>{{cite book |author=Kolata,Gina |title=Rethinking thin: The new science of weight loss - and the myths and realities of dieting |publisher=Picador |location= |year=2007 |pages= |isbn=0-312-42785-9}}</ref>。

某些药物可以导致体重增加和体质构成改变，這些藥物包括[[胰岛素|胰岛素]]、[[硫酰脲|硫酰脲]]、{{le|噻唑烷二酮|Thiazolidinedione}}、{{le|非典型抗精神病药|Atypical antipsychotic}}、[[抗抑郁药|抗抑郁药]]、[[类固醇|糖皮质激素]]、某些{{le|抗癫痫药|Anticonvulsant}}（比如[[苯妥英钠|苯妥英钠]]、[[丙戊酸钠|丙戊酸钠]]）、{{le|苯噻啶|Pizotifen}}以及某些剂型的{{le|激素类避孕药|Hormonal contraception}}<ref name=HaslamJames/>。

===社會因子===
<!--{{Main|Social determinants of obesity}}-->
[[File:Yamai_no_Soshi_-_Obesity.JPG|thumb]]
雖然基因對肥胖的影響很重要，但它無法解釋為何部分國家（甚至全球）的肥胖率正在大幅上升<ref>{{cite journal | author = Yach D, Stuckler D, Brownell KD | title = Epidemiologic and economic consequences of the global epidemics of obesity and diabetes | journal = Nat. Med. | volume = 12 | issue = 1 | pages = 62–6 | date = 2006-01 | pmid = 16397571 | doi = 10.1038/nm0106-62 | url =  }}</ref>。雖然對個人來說，熱量攝取高於消耗會帶來肥胖；但在社會層面上，造成熱量攝取與消耗消長的真正成因仍在爭論中，並有許多理論試圖找出原因，但多數人相信真正的原因是這許多因素的總和 。
[[社會階級|社會階級]]與BMI的關聯性強弱在世界各地有所不同。1989年的評論性文章指出[[已開發國家|已開發國家]]中社會地位較高的女性較不易有肥胖問題，但不同社會地位的男性的肥胖率則沒有顯著差異；在[[發展中國家|發展中國家]]，社會地位較高的女性、男性、以及兒童都有較高的肥胖率<ref>{{cite journal | author = Sobal J, Stunkard AJ | title = Socioeconomic status and obesity: A review of the literature | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_psychological-bulletin_1989-03_105_2/page/260 | journal = Psychol Bull | volume = 105 | issue = 2 | pages = 260–75 | date = 1989-03 | pmid = 2648443 | doi = 10.1037/0033-2909.105.2.260 | type = Review }}</ref>。該評論文章在2007年更新，發現肥胖與社會地位的關係雖然不變，但關聯性減弱，並認為關連性的減弱是受到全球化的影響<ref name=McLaren2007>{{cite journal | author = McLaren L | title = Socioeconomic status and obesity | journal = Epidemiol Rev | volume = 29 | issue =  | pages = 29–48 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17478442 | doi = 10.1093/epirev/mxm001 | type = Review }}</ref>。在已開發國家中，[[收入不平等|收入越不平均]]的地區，成人肥胖率與青少年過重率越高，這個現象在美國也能觀察到：在收入不平等的州，即使是較高社會地位的人也容易有肥胖問題<ref name="spirit">{{cite book|title=The Spirit Level: Why More Equal Societies Almost Always Do Better |last1=Wilkinson |first1=Richard  |last2=Pickett |first2=Kate |publisher=Allen Lane |location=London |isbn=978-1-84614-039-6 |year=2009 |pages=91–101}}</ref>。

BMI與社會地位的關係有許多解釋。有些人認為在已開發國家中，富人能消費營養較為均衡的食物，且維持纖細體態的社會壓力較大，維持[[體適能|體適能]]的機會與期待也都比較高；在[[未開發國家|未開發國家]]，認為負擔食物開銷的能力、高勞動帶來的高熱量消耗、以及對較胖體態的文化偏好都能解釋肥胖率與社會地位的關連<ref name=McLaren2007/>。對體重的態度也在肥胖的發生中佔一定角色，在朋友、兄弟姊妹、以及配偶的身上都能觀察到他們之間的BMI變化有關聯性<ref>{{cite journal | author = Christakis NA, Fowler JH | title = The Spread of Obesity in a Large Social Network over 32 Years | journal = New England Journal of Medicine | volume = 357 | issue = 4 | pages = 370–379 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17652652 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMsa066082 | type = Research Support }}</ref>。精神壓力及社會地位低似乎也會增加肥胖率<ref name="spirit" /><ref>{{cite journal | author = Björntorp P | title = Do stress reactions cause abdominal obesity and comorbidities? | journal = Obesity Reviews | volume = 2 | issue = 2 | pages = 73–86 | year = 2001 | pmid = 12119665 | doi = 10.1046/j.1467-789x.2001.00027.x }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Goodman E, Adler NE, Daniels SR, Morrison JA, Slap GB, Dolan LM | title = Impact of objective and subjective social status on obesity in a biracial cohort of adolescents | journal = Obesity Reviews | volume = 11 | issue = 8 | pages = 1018–26 | year = 2003 | pmid = 12917508 | doi = 10.1038/oby.2003.140 | type = Research Support }}</ref>。

吸菸對個人的體重有明顯影響。男性戒菸者十年內平均會增重4.4公斤（9.7磅），女性戒菸者則會增重5公斤（11.0磅）<ref>{{cite journal | author = Flegal KM, Troiano RP, Pamuk ER, Kuczmarski RJ, Campbell SM | title = The influence of smoking cessation on the prevalence of overweight in the United States | journal = N. Engl. J. Med. | volume = 333 | issue = 18 | pages = 1165–70 | date = 1995-11 | pmid = 7565970 | doi = 10.1056/NEJM199511023331801 | url = http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/full/333/18/1165 | access-date = 2016-01-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20030405192136/http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/full/333/18/1165 | archive-date = 2003-04-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但整體而言吸菸率的變化對整體的肥胖率並沒有明顯影響<ref>{{cite journal | author = Chiolero A, Faeh D, Paccaud F, Cornuz J | title = Consequences of smoking for body weight, body fat distribution, and insulin resistance | journal = Am. J. Clin. Nutr. | volume = 87 | issue = 4 | pages = 801–9 | date = 2008-04-01 | pmid = 18400700 | url = http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/87/4/801 | type = Review | access-date = 2016-01-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101009020301/http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/87/4/801 | archive-date = 2010-10-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

在美國，生子的數量與肥胖風險也有關。每生一個孩子，女性的肥胖風險就上升7%，男性則會上升4%<ref>{{cite journal | author = Weng HH, Bastian LA, Taylor DH, Moser BK, Ostbye T | title = Number of children associated with obesity in middle-aged women and men: results from the health and retirement study | journal = J Women's Health (Larchmt) | volume = 13 | issue = 1 | pages = 85–91 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15006281 | doi = 10.1089/154099904322836492 | type = Comparative Study }}</ref>。這個現象可能是因為在西方國家，家庭撫養的孩子越多，家長的運動量就越少<ref>{{cite journal | author = Bellows-Riecken KH, Rhodes RE | title = A birth of inactivity? A review of physical activity and parenthood | journal = Prev Med | volume = 46 | issue = 2 | pages = 99–110 | date = 2008-02 | pmid = 17919713 | doi = 10.1016/j.ypmed.2007.08.003 | type = Review }}</ref>。

在發展中國家，[[都市化|都市化]]在肥胖率上升的過程中扮演一定的角色。在中國，平均肥胖率只有不到5%，但在某些都市肥胖率卻高達20%以上<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.who.int/dietphysicalactivity/media/en/gsfs_obesity.pdf |title=Obesity and Overweight |format=PDF |publisher=[[World_Health_Organization|World Health Organization]] |accessdate=2009-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170713190601/http://www.who.int/dietphysicalactivity/media/en/gsfs_obesity.pdf |archive-date=2017-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。早年營養不良和發展中國家的肥胖率上升也有一定的關聯<ref name="DC2001">{{cite journal | author = Caballero B | title = Introduction. Symposium: Obesity in developing countries: biological and ecological factors | journal = J. Nutr. | volume = 131 | issue = 3 | pages = 866S–870S | date = 2001-03 | pmid = 11238776 | doi =  | url = http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/content/full/131/3/866S | type = Review | access-date = 2016-01-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090503054014/http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/content/full/131/3/866S | archive-date = 2009-05-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，營養不良時期造成的內分泌變化可能會誘使身體在有食物時傾向堆積脂肪<ref name="DC2001" />。

[[流行病學|流行病學]]資料指出[[認知障礙|認知障礙]]與肥胖風險相關<ref name="Smith2011">{{cite journal | author = Smith E, Hay P, Campbell L, Trollor JN | title = A review of the association between obesity and cognitive function across the lifespan: implications for novel approaches to prevention and treatment | journal = Obesity Reviews | volume = 12 | pages = 740–755 | year = 2011 | pmid = 21991597 | doi = 10.1111/j.1467-789X.2011.00920.x | url = http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1467-789X.2011.00920.x/abstract | issue = 9 | type = Review | access-date = 2016-01-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234812/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1467-789X.2011.00920.x/abstract | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但究竟是認知障礙造成肥胖，或者是反過來，則尚不明朗。

===感染性因素===
<!--{{See also|Infectobesity}}-->
感染性因素如何影響代謝的相關研究才剛起步。目前已經知道正常體重者與肥胖者身上的[[腸道菌叢|腸道菌叢]]組成是不同的，證據顯示腸道菌叢可以影響代謝能力。正常體重者與肥胖者有明顯的代謝能力差異，因此推測從腸道中吸收熱量的能力可能會影響肥胖的發生，但目前還不確定這些差異是否會直接造成肥胖，或者這些其實是肥胖造成的結果<ref>{{cite journal | author = DiBaise JK, Zhang H, Crowell MD, Krajmalnik-Brown R, Decker GA, Rittmann BE | title = Gut microbiota and its possible relationship with obesity | journal = Mayo Clinic proceedings. Mayo Clinic | volume = 83 | issue = 4 | pages = 460–9 | date = 2008-04 | pmid = 18380992 | doi = 10.4065/83.4.460 | type = Review }}</ref>。

在人類與其他數種動物身上也能觀察到[[病毒|病毒]]與肥胖的關聯，但還不清楚這與肥胖率的上升是否有關<ref>{{cite journal | author = Falagas ME, Kompoti M | title = Obesity and infection | journal = Lancet Infect Dis | volume = 6 | issue = 7 | pages = 438–46 | date = 2006-07 | pmid = 16790384 | doi = 10.1016/S1473-3099(06)70523-0 | url = | type = Review }}</ref>。

==病理生理學==
[[File:Fatmouse.jpg|thumb]]，因此體型明顯和右側的正常老鼠不同]]

肥胖的發生與維持有許多種可能的[[病理生理學|病理生理]]機轉<ref name="flier">{{cite journal | author = Flier JS | title = Obesity wars: Molecular progress confronts an expanding epidemic | journal = Cell | volume = 116 | issue = 2 | pages = 337–50 | year = 2004 | pmid = 14744442 | doi = 10.1016/S0092-8674(03)01081-X | type = Review }}</ref>，但這個研究領域一直乏人問津，在1994年時，弗萊德曼（{{lang|en|J. M. Friedman}}）的研究團隊才發現[[瘦蛋白|瘦素]]基因<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Zhang|first1=Y|last2=Proenca|first2=R|last3=Maffei|first3=M|last4=Barone|first4=M|last5=Leopold|first5=L|last6=Friedman|first6=JM|title=Positional cloning of the mouse obese gene and its human homologue.|journal=Nature|date=1994-12-01|volume=372|issue=6505|pages=425–32|doi=10.1038/372425a0|pmid=7984236|type=Research Support}}</ref>。弗萊德曼的研究團隊認為[[瘦蛋白|瘦素]]是影響飽足感的因子。實驗中發現{{link-en|胖胖鼠|ob/ob mouse}}（一種意外發現，具有過度食慾並且極端肥胖的實驗用小鼠）帶有突變[[瘦蛋白|瘦素]]基因，因此展現肥胖的表現型，這個結果開啟以[[瘦蛋白|瘦素]]來治療人類肥胖的可能性，但不久後卡羅（{{lang|en|J. F. Caro}}）的研究團隊就發現無法在肥胖的人身上找到任何瘦素基因的突變；另一方面，在肥胖者身上的[[瘦蛋白|瘦素]]基因表現量上升，反而指出了肥胖者身上可能有瘦素抵抗現象<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Considine|first1=RV|last2=Considine|first2=EL|last3=Williams|first3=CJ|last4=Nyce|first4=MR|last5=Magosin|first5=SA|last6=Bauer|first6=TL|last7=Rosato|first7=EL|last8=Colberg|first8=J|last9=Caro|first9=JF <!--exactly 9 authors--> |title=Evidence against either a premature stop codon or the absence of obese gene mRNA in human obesity.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-clinical-investigation_1995-06_95_6/page/2986|journal=The Journal of Clinical Investigation|date=1995-06|volume=95|issue=6|pages=2986–8|pmid=7769141|doi=10.1172/jci118007|pmc=295988|type=Research Support}}</ref>。在發現瘦素後，研究者陸續發現許多其他影響[[食慾|食慾]]、進食、[[脂肪組織|脂肪儲存]]、[[胰島素抗性|胰島素抗性]]的激素，舉例來說[[飢餓素|飢餓素]]、[[胰島素|胰島素]]、[[食慾素|食慾素]]、{{link-en|雙酪胺酸肽3-36|peptide YY}}、[[膽囊收縮素|膽囊收縮素]]、[[脂聯素|脂聯素]]等因子都是學者研究的對象。{{le|脂激素|Adipokine}}是由脂肪組織釋放出的訊息因子，它們的作用會影響許多肥胖相關的疾病。

一般認為[[瘦蛋白|瘦素]]與[[飢餓素|飢餓素]]在食慾的影響上扮演互補的角色。饑餓素由胃製造，負責調節短期的食慾變化，比方說在胃排空時進食並在胃裝滿時停止；而瘦素則是由脂肪組織製造，反映人體脂肪儲藏的總量，並調節長期食慾變化，比如說在脂肪儲藏量低時增加食量，並在儲藏量高時減少食量。雖然使用瘦素對一小部分瘦素缺乏的肥胖者有效，但目前認為絕大多數的肥胖者都有瘦素抗性，在他們的身體中也都已經有高濃度的瘦素<ref>{{cite journal | author = Hamann A, Matthaei S | title = Regulation of energy balance by leptin | journal = Exp. Clin. Endocrinol. Diabetes | volume = 104 | issue = 4 | pages = 293–300 | year = 1996 | pmid = 8886745 | doi = 10.1055/s-0029-1211457 | type = Review }}</ref>。瘦素抗性可以解釋為何使用瘦素無法有效減少多數肥胖者的食量<ref name="flier"/>。

[[File:Leptin.png|thumb]]的分子模型]]
[[瘦蛋白|瘦素]]與[[飢餓素|飢餓素]]雖然由周邊組織製造和分泌，它們仍然要透過影響[[中樞神經系統|中樞神經系統]]才可以發揮調節食慾的功能。更精確的說，它們以及其他食慾相關激素會作用在[[下視丘|下視丘]]，這是腦中負責管理進食與能量消耗的中心。下視丘中有幾個迴路在調節食慾中扮演重要角色。{{link-en|黑皮質素|melanocortin}}路徑是目前了解最透徹的食慾訊息傳遞分子<ref name="flier"/>，它從下視丘的[[弓狀核|弓狀核]]分泌至{{link-en|下視丘外核|lateral hypothalamus}}（LH）與{{link-en|下視丘腹中核|ventromedial nucleus}}（VMH），這兩個核分別是腦中的進食中樞與飽足中樞<ref>{{cite book|author=Boulpaep, Emile L.; Boron, Walter F. |title=Medical physiology: A cellular and molecular approach |url=https://archive.org/details/medicalphysiolog0000boro_a6j9 |publisher=Saunders |location=Philadelphia |year=2003 |page=[https://archive.org/details/medicalphysiolog0000boro_a6j9/page/n1227 1227] |isbn=0-7216-3256-4}}</ref>。

[[弓狀核|弓狀核]]內含有兩群[[神經元|神經元]]<ref name="flier"/>：第一群同時表現{{link-en|神經肽Y|neuropeptide Y}}（NPY）與{{link-en|刺豚鼠關聯肽|agouti-related peptide}}（AgRP），它們會刺激{{link-en|下視丘外核|lateral hypothalamus}}並抑制{{link-en|下視丘腹中核|ventromedial nucleus}}；第二群則表現[[鴉片黑皮質素原|鴉片黑皮質素原]]（POMC）與{{le|古柯鹼-安非他命關聯轉錄因子|cocaine- and amphetamine-regulated transcript}}（CART），並會刺激{{link-en|下視丘腹中核|ventromedial nucleus}}及抑制下視丘外核。因此表現NPY / AgRP的神經元會促進進食並抑制飽足感；而表現POMC / CART的神經元則相反地會抑制進食並激發飽足感。在[[弓狀核|弓狀核]]中的兩組神經元都受[[瘦蛋白|瘦素]]調控：瘦素會抑制表現NPY / AgRP的神經元並刺激表現POMC / CART的神經元。因此如果瘦素相關的訊息傳導不足（可能由於瘦素不足或是瘦素抵抗），就會造成食慾提升而過度進食，這也能解釋某些基因疾病與後天狀況造成的肥胖<ref name="flier"/>。

==公共衛生議題==
[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]（WHO）預測[[過重|過重]]與肥胖將在近期超過[[傳染病|傳染病]]、[[營養不良|營養不良]]等以往造成健康狀況不佳的主因，成為健康狀況不佳的最重要原因<ref>{{Cite report|author=World Health Organization|authorlink=World Health Organization|coauthors=|date=2000|title=Obesity: preventing and managing the global epidemic|url=http://www.who.int/iris/handle/10665/42330|publisher=World Health Organization|page=1-2|docket=|accessdate=2014-02-01|quote=|archive-date=2021-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210828192922/https://apps.who.int/iris/handle/10665/42330|dead-url=no}}</ref>。肥胖問題在公共衛生與公共政策上的重要性來自於它的盛行率、造成的成本、以及對健康的影響<ref>{{cite book|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK44206/|title=The Surgeon General's Call to Action to Prevent and Decrease Overweight and Obesity|publisher=U.S. Dept. of Health and Human Services, Public Health Service, Office of Surgeon General|year=2001|isbn=978-0-16-051005-2|author=Satcher D|access-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124223808/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK44206/|archive-date=2017-01-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|美國預防服務工作小組|United States Preventive Services Task Force}}建議對所有成年人進行肥胖篩檢，並對肥胖者進行行為介入與追蹤<ref>{{cite journal|title=Screening for and management of obesity in adults: U.S. Preventive Services Task Force recommendation statement|author=Moyer VA|date=2012-09-04|journal=Annals of Internal Medicine|issue=5|doi=10.7326/0003-4819-157-5-201209040-00475|volume=157|pages=373–8|type=Practice Guideline|pmid=22733087}}</ref>。公共衛生手段試圖理解並修正造成肥胖人口上升的環境因素，並提出方案以改正造成食物熱量攝取過高與運動量不足的問題。美國目前採行的方案包括聯邦出資的校園飲食計畫、限制直接向孩童行銷[[垃圾食物|垃圾食物]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/07/18/business/18food.html|title=Limiting Ads of Junk Food to Children|date=2007-07-18|work=New York Times|accessdate=2008-07-24|author=Brook Barnes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210081923/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/07/18/business/18food.html|archive-date=2008-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及減少校園內的含糖飲料<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.healthfinder.gov/news/newsstory.aspx?docID=625759|title=Fewer Sugary Drinks Key to Weight Loss - healthfinder.gov|accessdate=2009-10-18|work=U.S. Department of Health and Human Services|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121116045620/http://www.healthfinder.gov/news/newsstory.aspx?docID=625759|archive-date=2012-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外在都市設計上也增加公園的可近性並增加人行道-{}-路。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Indicators of activity-friendly communities: An evidence-based consensus process|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-preventive-medicine_2006-12_31_6/page/530|author=Brennan Ramirez LK, Hoehner CM, Brownson RC, Cook R, Orleans CT, Hollander M, Barker DC, Bors P, Ewing R, Killingsworth R, Petersmarck K, Schmid T, Wilkinson W|date=2006-12|journal=Am J Prev Med|issue=6|doi=10.1016/j.amepre.2006.07.026|volume=31|pages=530–32|type=Research Support|pmid=17169714}}</ref>。世衛組織建議各國徵收[[含糖飲料稅|含糖飲料稅]]，以減少攝取[[游離糖|游離糖]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO urges global action to curtail consumption and health impacts of sugary drinks|url=http://www.who.int/en/news-room/detail/11-10-2016-who-urges-global-action-to-curtail-consumption-and-health-impacts-of-sugary-drinks|website=WHO|date=11 October 2016|accessdate=7 November 2018|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181030113009/http://www.who.int/en/news-room/detail/11-10-2016-who-urges-global-action-to-curtail-consumption-and-health-impacts-of-sugary-drinks|archive-date=2018-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>

許多國家或組織針對肥胖問題發表報告。1998年時美國發表第一篇聯邦肥胖治療指引《成人過重與肥胖之診斷、評估與治療臨床指引：證據報告》<ref name="nhlbi">{{cite book|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/obesity/ob_gdlns.pdf|title=Clinical Guidelines on the Identification, Evaluation, and Treatment of Overweight and Obesity in Adults|publisher=International Medical Publishing, Inc|year=1998|isbn=1-58808-002-1|location=|format=PDF|oclc=|author=National Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute|access-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111108181439/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/obesity/ob_gdlns.pdf|archive-date=2011-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>；{{le|加拿大肥胖網路|Canadian Obesity Network}}於2006年發表《加拿大成人與兒童肥胖預防暨治療臨床指引》，這是一份完整的實證醫學臨床指引，內容包括成人及兒童過重與肥胖的治療與預防<ref name="CADG20062">{{cite journal|title=2006 Canadian clinical practice guidelines on the management and prevention of obesity in adults and children summary|author=Lau DC, Douketis JD, Morrison KM, Hramiak IM, Sharma AM, Ur E|url=http://www.cmaj.ca/cgi/content/full/176/8/S1|date=2007-04|journal=CMAJ|issue=8|doi=10.1503/cmaj.061409|volume=176|pages=S1–13|type=Practice Guideline, Review|pmc=1839777|pmid=17420481|access-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610222726/http://www.cmaj.ca/cgi/content/full/176/8/S1|archive-date=2011-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

英國[[倫敦皇家內科醫學院|皇家內科醫學院]]、{{le|英國公共衛生學院|Faculty of Public Health|公共衛生學院}}與{{le|皇家兒科暨兒童健康學院|Royal College of Paediatrics and Child Health}}於2004年發表《堆積如山的問題》（Storing up Problems）強調英國日漸嚴重的肥胖問題<ref>{{cite book|title=Storing up problems; the medical case for a slimmer nation|date=2004-02-11|publisher=Royal College of Physicians|isbn=1-86016-200-2|location=London}}</ref>。同年，[[英國下議院|英國下議院]]{{le|健康遴選委員會|Health Select Committee}}發表了一篇針對「肥胖問題對英國健康與社會的衝擊」的報告，並號稱是該議題中「史上最完整的調查報告」，內文也包括了可能的解決手段<ref name="GB20042">{{cite book|url=http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200304/cmselect/cmhealth/23/2302.htm|title=Obesity – Volume 1 – HCP 23-I, Third Report of session 2003–04. Report, together with formal minutes|date=2004-05|publisher=TSO (The Stationery Office)|accessdate=2007-12-17|isbn=978-0-215-01737-6|location=London, UK|author=Great Britain Parliament House of Commons Health Committee|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110124035759/http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200304/cmselect/cmhealth/23/2302.htm|archive-date=2011-01-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|英國國家健康與照顧卓越研究院|National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence}}在2006年發表了肥胖診斷與治療的臨床指引，以及針對非醫療組織（比方說地方政府）的策略指引<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nice.org.uk/nicemedia/pdf/CG43NICEGuideline.pdf|title=Obesity: guidance on the prevention, identification, assessment and management of overweight and obesity in adults and children|accessdate=2009-04-08|year=2006|format=PDF|work=National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence(NICE)|publisher=National Health Services (NHS)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090413050504/http://www.nice.org.uk/nicemedia/pdf/CG43NICEGuideline.pdf|archive-date=2009-04-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|國王基金會|King's Fund}}的{{le|德里克·萬利斯|Derek Wanless}}爵士於2007年發表報告，警告若不採取對策，肥胖問題將拖垮英國[[國民保健署|國民保健署]]<ref>{{cite book|title=Our Future Health Secured? A review of NHS funding and performance|last=Wanless|first=Sir Derek|last2=Appleby|first2=John|last3=Harrison|first3=Anthony|last4=Patel|first4=Darshan|publisher=The King's Fund|year=2007|isbn=1-85717-562-X|location=London, UK}}</ref>。

目前的主流觀點認為，對抗肥胖症需有一套完整的對策。因此，肥胖政策與行動框架（Obesity Policy Action (OPA) framework）將對策區分為：上游、中游、與下游策略。上游策略主要試圖改變社會；中游策略則試圖改變個人行為以預防肥胖；下游策略則是治療已經肥胖的人口<ref>{{cite journal|title=Obesity Policy Action framework and analysis grids for a comprehensive policy approach to reducing obesity|author=Sacks G, Swinburn B, Lawrence M|date=2009-01|journal=Obes Rev|issue=1|doi=10.1111/j.1467-789X.2008.00524.X|volume=10|pages=76–86|pmid=18761640}}</ref>。

== 治疗方法 ==
{{Main|减肥}}
肥胖症的治療方式包括行為學療法、藥物治療和手術。行為學療法是最主要的治疗方式，也就是透過改變飲食習慣、飲食結構以及運動來達到減肥的目的<ref name=CADG2006/><ref name="Chien">{{cite web|url=http://hospital.kingnet.com.tw/essay/essay.html?pid=41010|title=健康減重|accessdate=2016-03-16|publisher=國家網路醫院|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316105556/http://hospital.kingnet.com.tw/essay/essay.html?pid=41010|archivedate=2016-03-16|author1=簡郁芬|website=|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。合理的饮食控制能在短期内使体重明显下降<ref name="Strychar">{{cite journal |author=Strychar I |title=Diet in the management of weight loss |journal=CMAJ |volume=174 |issue=1 |pages=56–63 |date=2006-01 |pmid=16389240 |pmc=1319349 |doi=10.1503/cmaj.045037 |url=http://www.cmaj.ca/cgi/content/full/174/1/56 |access-date=2008-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610222708/http://www.cmaj.ca/cgi/content/full/174/1/56 |archive-date=2011-06-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但要維持減重的成果經常相當困難，常需要搭配運動以及配合低热量饮食的生活方式<ref>{{cite journal |author=Shick SM, Wing RR, Klem ML, McGuire MT, Hill JO, Seagle H |title=Persons successful at long-term weight loss and maintenance continue to consume a low-energy, low-fat diet |journal=J Am Diet Assoc |volume=98 |issue=4 |pages=408–13 |date=1998-04|pmid=9550162 |doi=10.1016/S0002-8223(98)00093-5}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Tate DF, Jeffery RW, Sherwood NE, Wing RR |title=Long-term weight losses associated with prescription of higher physical activity goals. Are higher levels of physical activity protective against weight regain? |journal=Am. J. Clin. Nutr. |volume=85 |issue=4 |pages=954–9 |date=2007-04 |pmid=17413092 |url=http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/85/4/954 |access-date=2008-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100606051612/http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/85/4/954 |archive-date=2010-06-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。各種低[[碳水化合物|碳水化合物]]與低脂飲食對健康的幫助似乎沒有差別<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Johnston|first1=Bradley C.|last2=Kanters|first2=Steve|last3=Bandayrel|first3=Kristofer|last4=Wu|first4=Ping|last5=Naji|first5=Faysal|last6=Siemieniuk|first6=Reed A.|last7=Ball|first7=Geoff D. C.|last8=Busse|first8=Jason W.|last9=Thorlund|first9=Kristian|last10=Guyatt|first10=Gordon|last11=Jansen|first11=Jeroen P.|last12=Mills|first12=Edward J.|title=Comparison of Weight Loss Among Named Diet Programs in Overweight and Obese Adults|journal=JAMA|date=2014-09-03|volume=312|issue=9|pages=923|doi=10.1001/jama.2014.10397}}</ref>。在心臟疾病與糖尿病的風險控制上，這些飲食策略也表現地不相上下<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Naude|first1=CE|last2=Schoonees|first2=A|last3=Senekal|first3=M|last4=Young|first4=T|last5=Garner|first5=P|last6=Volmink|first6=J|title=Low carbohydrate versus isoenergetic balanced diets for reducing weight and cardiovascular risk: a systematic review and meta-analysis.|journal=PLOS ONE|date=2014|volume=9|issue=7|pages=e100652|pmid=25007189|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0100652|type=Research Support}}</ref>。長期的減重成功率與生活形態改變率並不高，約為2-20%<ref>{{cite journal|authors=Wing RR, Phelan S |title=Long-term weight loss maintenance |journal=The American Journal of Clinical Nutrition |volume=82 |issue=1 Suppl |pages=222S–225S |year=2005 |pmid=16002825 |doi= |url= |type=Review}}</ref>。一般只有20%的人能长期保持体重不反弹<ref>{{cite journal |author= |title=Science-Based Solutions to Obesity: What are the Roles of Academia, Government, Industry, and Health Care? Proceedings of a symposium, Boston, Massachusetts, USA, 10–11 2004-03 and Anaheim, California, USA, 2004-10-02 |journal=Am. J. Clin. Nutr. |volume=82 |issue=1 Suppl |pages=207S–273S |date=2005-07 |pmid=16002825 |url=http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/82/1/222S |access-date=2008-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101007093102/http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/82/1/222S |archive-date=2010-10-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。更进一步的调查发现，67%减重超过体重10%的患者，能在此后一年内维持该体重或者保持继续减重的趋势<ref>{{cite journal |author=Weiss EC, Galuska DA, Kettel Khan L, Gillespie C, Serdula MK |title=Weight regain in U.S. adults who experienced substantial weight loss, 1999–2002 |journal=Am J Prev Med |volume=33 |issue=1 |pages=34–40 |date=2007-07 |pmid=17572309 |doi=10.1016/j.amepre.2007.02.040 |url=}}</ref>。体重平均减少大于3kg或者减重大于总体重3%的患者能在5年内保持这一水平<ref>{{cite journal |author=Anderson JW, Konz EC, Frederich RC, Wood CL |title=Long-term weight-loss maintenance: A meta-analysis of US studies |journal=Am. J. Clin. Nutr. |volume=74 |issue=5 |pages=579–84 |date=2001-11 |pmid=11684524 |url=http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/74/5/579 |access-date=2008-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101009033343/http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/74/5/579 |archive-date=2010-10-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

减肥的好处显而易见，在一项前瞻性调查研究中，主动减肥，不论其体重下降的程度，都能使任何原因所导致的死亡率减少20%<ref>{{cite journal |author=Williamson DF, Pamuk E, Thun M, Flanders D, Byers T, Heath C |title=Prospective study of intentional weight loss and mortality in never-smoking overweight US white women aged 40–64 years |journal=Am. J. Epidemiol. |volume=141 |issue=12 |pages=1128–41 |date=1995-06 |pmid=7771451}}</ref>。若要控制[[懷孕|懷孕]]期間的體重增加與改善母嬰健康，透過飲食與生活形態的調整是有效的<ref>{{cite journal | author = Thangaratinam S, Rogozinska E, Jolly K, Glinkowski S, Roseboom T, Tomlinson JW, Kunz R, Mol BW, Coomarasamy A, Khan KS | title = Effects of interventions in pregnancy on maternal weight and obstetric outcomes: meta-analysis of randomised evidence | journal = BMJ (Clinical research ed.) | volume = 344 | pages = e2088 | date = 2012-05-16 | pmid = 22596383 | pmc = 3355191 | doi = 10.1136/bmj.e2088 | type = Meta-analysis }}</ref>。若心臟病患者有肥胖以及其他疾病風險因子，會建議接受密集的行為諮詢<ref>{{cite journal|last1=LeFevre|first1=Michael L.|title=Behavioral Counseling to Promote a Healthful Diet and Physical Activity for Cardiovascular Disease Prevention in Adults With Cardiovascular Risk Factors: U.S. Preventive Services Task Force Recommendation Statement|journal=Annals of Internal Medicine|date=2014-08-26|doi=10.7326/M14-1796|volume=161|pages=587}}</ref>。

=== 饮食控制 ===
控制饮食的方法一般分为如下四类：低脂饮食，低碳水化合物饮食，低热量饮食以及极低热量饮食。<ref name=Strychar/>一份針對六份隨機控制試驗所做出的[[後設分析|後設分析]]發現主要的[[節食|節食]]方法（低熱量、低碳水化合物及低脂）在減肥效果上沒有任何差異，都能順利減少二至四公斤。<ref name=Strychar/>

* 低脂饮食：主要是减少食物中脂肪的含量，但不减少摄入食物的总量。该方法是{{le|美国国家胆固醇教育计划|National Cholesterol Education Program}}中的第1步和第2步。16个试验（持续时间2-12个月不等）的 [[後設分析|後設分析]]结果显示，低脂饮食能使体重减少3.2公斤。<ref name=Strychar/>

* [[低碳水化合物饮食|低碳水化合物饮食]]：指增加食物中脂肪或脂肪和蛋白质的比例，比如[[食肉减肥法|Atkins减肥法]]和{{le|高蛋白质饮食法|High-protein diet}}。这种方法非常流行，但腎功能略差就不適用（許多人腎功能稍差，但他們沒有任何症狀），且此方法也不为美国心脏协会所推荐。据研究，该方法造成体重下降的原理是使饱足感增加，导致能量摄入减少<!--。有些研究指出低碳水化合物饮食并未发现有不良反应--><ref>{{cite journal |author=Bravata DM, Sanders L, Huang J, ''et al.'' |title=Efficacy and safety of low-carbohydrate diets: A systematic review |journal=JAMA |volume=289 |issue=14 |pages=1837–50 |date=2003-04 |pmid=12684364 |doi=10.1001/jama.289.14.1837}}</ref>。

* 低[[升糖指數|升糖指數]]、低[[升糖負荷|升糖負荷]]飲食：此方法的理論基礎在於血液中[[胰島素|胰島素]]過高與波動會造成食量上升與脂肪堆積，因此認為減少糖分攝取能避免肥胖症發生<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Glycemic index and obesity|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12081852|last=Brand-Miller|first=Janette C.|last2=Holt|first2=Susanna H. A.|date=2002-07-01|journal=The American Journal of Clinical Nutrition|issue=1|volume=76|pages=281S–5S|issn=0002-9165|pmid=12081852|last3=Pawlak|first3=Dorota B.|last4=McMillan|first4=Joanna|author=|access-date=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919090657/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12081852|archive-date=2016-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* 低热量饮食：指每天只摄入800-1500kcal热量，形成能量负平衡，每周可使体重下降0.5公斤。{{le|美國衛生研究院|The National Institutes of Health}}回顾分析了34个[[随机对照试验|随机对照试验]]，发现该方法能在3-12个月内减少8%的体重。<ref name=Strychar/>

* 极低热量饮食：指每日只摄入400-800kcal热量，严格限制蛋白质、脂肪和碳水化合物的摄入，使個體处于长期饥饿状态，每周能使体重下降1.5-2.5公斤。但是會引起[[瘦素|瘦素]]减少、[[痛风|痛风]]风险增加、和[[电解质平衡紊乱|电解质平衡紊乱]]等不良反应，因此不受广泛推荐。尝试该方法的患者需要在医生的指导下进行，并严格预防并发症的发生。<ref name=Strychar/>

===藥物治療===
市面已有三種減肥藥已有證據可以長期使用，分別是[[奧利司他|奧利司他]]（羅氏鮮）、{{link-en|洛卡色林|lorcaserin}}（Belviq）以及{{le|芬他命與托吡酯複方|Phentermine/topiramate}}（Qsymia）<ref name="Yan2014">{{cite journal | author = Yanovski SZ, Yanovski JA | title = Long-term drug treatment for obesity: a systematic and clinical review. | journal = JAMA: the Journal of the American Medical Association | volume = 311 | issue = 1 | pages = 74–86 | date = 2014-01-01 | pmid = 24231879 | doi = 10.1001/jama.2013.281361 | pmc=3928674 |  type = Review }}</ref>。[[奧利司他|奧利司他]]能少量減輕體重，平均約為在一到四年間減少2.9公斤<ref name="Orli07">{{cite journal | author = Rucker D, Padwal R, Li SK, Curioni C, Lau DC | title = Long term pharmacotherapy for obesity and overweight: updated meta-analysis | journal = BMJ | volume = 335 | issue = 7631 | pages = 1194–99 | year = 2007 | pmid = 18006966 | pmc = 2128668 | doi = 10.1136/bmj.39385.413113.25 | url = http://www.bmj.com/cgi/content/full/335/7631/1194 | type = Meta-analysis | access-date = 2016-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090530152818/http://www.bmj.com/cgi/content/full/335/7631/1194 | archive-date = 2009-05-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但有相當高的機會產生腸胃副作用<ref name=Orli07/>，它對腎臟的影響也受到質疑<ref>{{cite web |last=Wood |first=Shelley |title=Diet Drug Orlistat Linked to Kidney, Pancreas Injuries |url=http://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/740855?src=mp&spon=30 |work=Medscape |publisher=Medscape News |accessdate=2011-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510133448/http://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/740855?src=mp&spon=30 |archive-date=2012-05-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外兩種藥物則只在美國上市<ref name=EMA2013>{{cite journal | author = Wolfe SM | title = When EMA and FDA decisions conflict: differences in patients or in regulation? | journal = BMJ (Clinical research ed.) | volume = 347 | pages = f5140 | date = 2013-08-21 | pmid = 23970394 | doi = 10.1136/bmj.f5140 }}</ref>。洛卡色林平均能在一年內比安慰劑多減少3.1公斤的體重（3%體重）<ref>{{cite journal | author = Bays HE | title = Lorcaserin: drug profile and illustrative model of the regulatory challenges of weight-loss drug development | journal = Expert review of cardiovascular therapy | volume = 9 | issue = 3 | pages = 265–77 | date = 2011-03 | pmid = 21438803 | doi = 10.1586/erc.10.22 | type = Review }}</ref>，但可能會引發心臟瓣膜的問題<ref name=EMA2013/>。芬他命與托吡酯同時使用也具有某種程度的減重效果<ref>{{cite journal | author = Bays HE, Gadde KM | title = Phentermine/topiramate for weight reduction and treatment of adverse metabolic consequences in obesity | journal = Drugs Today | volume = 47 | issue = 12 | pages = 903–14 | date = 2011-12 | pmid = 22348915 | doi = 10.1358/dot.2011.47.12.1718738 | type = Review }}</ref>，但使用這兩種藥物同樣與心臟問題有關聯<ref name=EMA2013/>。現下還沒有資料能闡明這些減重藥物對肥胖的長期併發症（比方說心血管疾病與死亡）的影響<ref name=Yan2014/>。

===減肥手術===
對肥胖最有效的治療是[[減肥手術|減肥手術]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Colquitt|first1=JL|last2=Pickett|first2=K|last3=Loveman|first3=E|last4=Frampton|first4=GK|title=Surgery for weight loss in adults|journal=The Cochrane database of systematic reviews|date=2014-08-08|volume=8|pages=CD003641|pmid=25105982|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD003641.pub4 | type=Meta-analysis, Review}}</ref>。嚴重肥胖者接受手術後能夠長期減輕體重、改善肥胖相關問題<ref name=Chang2013>{{cite journal | author = Chang SH, Stoll CR, Song J, Varela JE, Eagon CJ, Colditz GA | title = The effectiveness and risks of bariatric surgery: an updated systematic review and meta-analysis, 2003-2012 | journal = JAMA Surgery | volume = 149 | issue = 3 | pages = 275–87 | year = 2014 | pmid = 24352617 | doi = 10.1001/jamasurg.2013.3654 | type = Meta-analysis, Review }}</ref>、並降低死亡率。一項研究指出手術能在十年間減輕患者14%-25%的體重（視手術方法而定），且相對於一般減重方法，還能減低29%的死亡率<ref>{{cite journal | author = Sjöström L, Narbro K, Sjöström CD, Karason K, Larsson B, Wedel H, Lystig T, Sullivan M, Bouchard C, Carlsson B, Bengtsson C, Dahlgren S, Gummesson A, Jacobson P, Karlsson J, Lindroos AK, Lönroth H, Näslund I, Olbers T, Stenlöf K, Torgerson J, Agren G, Carlsson LM | title = Effects of bariatric surgery on mortality in Swedish obese subjects | journal = N. Engl. J. Med. | volume = 357 | issue = 8 | pages = 741–52 | date = 2007-08 | pmid = 17715408 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMoa066254 | type = Research Support }}</ref> 。不過手術併發症的發生率為17%，並且有7%的病人需要接受第二次手術<ref name=Chang2013/>。因為手術的花費與風險，研究者們正在尋找侵入性較低卻同樣有效的治療方法，比如說在胃中置入佔空間的物體（氣球）來減少胃容量<ref>{{cite web |last=Weintraub |first=Karen |title=New allies in war on weight |url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/business/2014/06/29/novel-ways-lose-weight-include-stomach-gel-electrical-impulses/LLzowmiW9d8yZsXXiHSOWN/story.html |work=The Boston Globe |publisher=The Boston Globe |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630094620/http://www.bostonglobe.com/business/2014/06/29/novel-ways-lose-weight-include-stomach-gel-electrical-impulses/LLzowmiW9d8yZsXXiHSOWN/story.html |archive-date=2014-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

