在[[近代史|近代]]以前雖然就已經認為肥胖會造成健康問題，但肥胖並不常見，只發生在少數的菁英階級身上。隨著物質生活日益富足，肥胖影響的人數也逐漸增多<ref name=Haslam2007/>。1997年[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]將肥胖視為全球性的流行病<ref name=Caballero/>。到了2008年，[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]估計至少有五億的成人（大於10%）有肥胖問題，而女性的肥胖問題又比男性嚴重<ref name=WHO2009a>{{cite web |url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs311/en/index.html |title=Obesity and overweight |work=World Health Organization |accessdate=2009-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090410205744/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs311/en/index.html |archive-date=2009-04-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在五十至六十歲前，肥胖率都會隨著年齡上升<ref name = "Kopelman2005"/>{{rp|5}}。而[[美國|美國]]、[[澳洲|澳洲]]及[[加拿大|加拿大]]的嚴重肥胖比率甚至上升得比整體肥胖率還快<ref name=morbid2007/><ref name="pmid24351678">{{cite journal | author = Howard NJ, Taylor AW, Gill TK, Chittleborough CR | title = Severe obesity: Investigating the socio-demographics within the extremes of body mass index | journal = Obesity Research & Clinical Practice | volume = 2 | issue = 1 | pages = I–II | year = 2008 | pmid = 24351678 | doi = 10.1016/j.orcp.2008.01.001 }}</ref><ref name=Tjepkema2005/>。

以往認為肥胖只是已開發國家的文明病，但事實上，開發中國家和已開發國家的肥胖比率都在上升<ref name=EuroG2008>{{cite journal | author = Tsigos C, Hainer V, Basdevant A, Finer N, Fried M, Mathus-Vliegen E, Micic D, Maislos M, Roman G, Schutz Y, Toplak H, Zahorska-Markiewicz B | title = Management of Obesity in Adults: European Clinical Practice Guidelines | journal = The European Journal of Obesity | volume = 1 | issue = 2 | pages = 106–16 | date = 2008-04 | pmid = 20054170 | doi = 10.1159/000126822 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/40870108_Management_of_Obesity_in_Adults_European_Clinical_Practice_Guidelines | access-date = 2016-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160911130944/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/40870108_Management_of_Obesity_in_Adults_European_Clinical_Practice_Guidelines | archive-date = 2016-09-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，城市地區的上升比例更為顯著<ref name=WHO2009a/>。除了[[撒哈拉以南非洲|撒哈拉以南非洲]]、部份[[最不发达国家|赤貧國家]]和東亞的[[日本|日本]]與[[韓國|韓國]]之外，肥胖在世界各地都已是常見疾病<ref name=HaslamJames/>。
